{"url": "https://www.liveabout.com/how-to-wear-it-flare-jeans-2040347", "text": "It\u2019s hard to avoid the ongoing debate between skinny versus wide-leg jeans. And yet, we see no reason to choose sides when a denim collection can be well rounded with various silhouette and fit options. That is why it may be worth considering a trend that falls somewhere in the middle by way of retro flare jeans.\n\nWhile flares do come packed with '60s and '70s references\u2014some will have fond memories of the trend\u2019s \u201890s return as well\u2014 today, the wide-legged jean shape doesn\u2019t necessarily give off an overtly flower-child or disco aesthetic. Instead, their slight bell shape provides a unique and playful detail to your favorite outfits, including something as classic as jeans and a T-shirt. There\u2019s also the option of the cropped mini flare for a more modern approach that complements everything from sneakers to your most strappy party heels. Ahead, peruse 10 flare outfits that have a hint of nostalgia but are undeniably trendy now.", "images": ["https://www.byrdie.com/thmb/8FoT4HEr8wI2sbL9cM0G6uL-RwE=/450x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/f10-d2efa84eed2a4ae8928a243a38acc468.jpg", "https://www.byrdie.com/thmb/-owqU99KHfG2Sdl-T8GFHUzSVTk=/300x240/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Byr_Ed_Picks_Primary-943e7e7c56584c18a5c7cc7a50d256ce.jpg", "https://www.byrdie.com/thmb/qqls0lsoQSq6Nnb2sHYW8wrB9uI=/450x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/f15-fee050628a0c43b0953015d461b4f936.jpg", "https://www.byrdie.com/thmb/f8gsYUmizf3JxPZBssPSQbk7aE0=/300x240/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/byrdie-update-best-designer-jeans-tout-eaceb94c464d42a7b31e01da854a9ae2.jpg", "https://www.byrdie.com/thmb/fFCoLOeSbou2b-ZkcuYRFXVFxLo=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/flarejeans1primary-fc35084ea46740c49aab994575ae76c4.jpg", "https://www.byrdie.com/thmb/uIHN_CB8clvaCW1QpF5Hl-dui7Y=/450x0/f